":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20190307/20627455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F20627455&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakdlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=f8939382\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F20627455&h=ddda922d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20190307/20627455</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n「初心」是中文詞語，不可拱手讓與中共。請看民國初年蔡東藩《後漢通俗演義》第六十七回，曹操不同意另立君主，對袁紹說：「諸君如欲北面（北面事新主），我卻仍然西向（忠於被董卓挾持西去的獻帝），不改初心。」又請看明朝洪應明《菜根譚．概論》：「事窮勢蹙之人，當原（體諒）其初心；功成行滿之士，要觀其末路（看能否善始善終）。」還有晉朝干寶《搜神記》卷十五，王道平到意中人墳前哭祭說：「不契於初心（未能如我們當年所願，結髮為夫妻），生死永訣。」「初衷」也是「初心」的意思。"},{"pid":"f144c7a2214a1129ff26674d5fe8435b6e1a6199","tid":1292029,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"抽埋林奠水又同你講咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實依個字又有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c87f93414379e48cf4cff332c01fb8f4f88958e","tid":1292029,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af9b906a752fa4f185d4cabd4566ee023037b852","tid":1292029,"uid":1646,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/201